---

<Layout title="Photography | Amitoj Singh" description="Visual explorations. Seeing as practice.">
  <section class="container-zen section-zen">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <h1 class="mb-8 text-balance">Photography</h1>

      <div class="accent-line mb-8"></div>

      <p class="text-lg text-ink-light mb-6">
        Seeing as practice. Light as language.
      </p>

      <p class="text-ink-light">
        [Placeholder: How photography fits into the broader work. The contemplative
        dimension of visual attention. What you tend to photograph and why.]
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container-zen section-zen border-t border-oat-300">
    <h2 class="text-2xl mb-8">Gallery</h2>

    <div class="photo-grid">
      {galleryImages.map((image) => (
        <figure class="photo-item">
          <div class="photo-placeholder">
            <span class="text-ink-muted text-sm">{image.title}</span>
          </div>
          <figcaption class="text-ink-muted text-xs mt-2">
            {image.title}
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      ))}
    </div>

    <p class="text-ink-muted text-sm mt-8">
      Gallery currently showing placeholders. Images coming soon.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="container-zen section-zen border-t border-oat-300">
    <h2 class="text-2xl mb-8">Approach</h2>

    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <p class="text-ink-light mb-6">
        [Placeholder: Your photographic philosophy. What draws your eye.
        The relationship between photography and contemplative practice.]
      </p>

      <p class="text-ink-light">
        [Placeholder: Equipment preferences, if relevant. Favorite subjects
        or locations. How the practice has evolved over time.]
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container-zen section-zen border-t border-oat-300 bg-oat-100">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl mb-6">Inquiries</h2>

      <p class="text-ink-light mb-8">
        For prints, licensing, or collaboration inquiries, please get in touch.
      </p>

      <a href="/contact" class="text-ink hover:text-ink-light no-underline">
        Contact &rarr;
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .photo-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .photo-item {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .photo-placeholder {
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    background-color: #EBE3D4; /* oat-300 */
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border: 1px solid #EBE3D4; /* oat-300 */
  }

  /* When real images are added, use this class */
  .photo-item img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .photo-item:hover img {
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .photo-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }
</style>
